    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 4-1 at this model risk level. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 across all operating points confirms acceptability relative to predicate device. Package is submitted under ProfileMinimal with hash integrity protection; digital signature is pending completion of the institutional signature workflow.",
